{"tid":2364552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報鄭重闢謠：河北現在疫情絕對與當初武漢不同！","createTime":"2021-01-13T05:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T06:47:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3d955aadc2c411e4a77065b52016690febbfdd6c","tid":2364552,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">多名專家接受《環球時報》採訪：河北三地封城，為何與當初武漢不同</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球時報作者：李司坤 晨陽<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-13 06:48<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報記者 李司坤 環球時報特約記者 晨陽】<span class=\"red\">由於疫情依然在擴散，河北省12日決定石家莊市、邢台市、廊坊市封城，人員、車輛非必要不外出。此前黑龍江省綏化市望奎縣也已於11日宣布封城。</span>在部分民眾心中，接連不斷的封城讓人回想起去年年初的情景，難道疫情已經擴散得如此厲害了嗎？多名接受《環球時報》記者採訪的專家12日表示，總體上看，<span class=\"red\">現在的疫情遠沒有去年武漢封城那麼嚴重。</span>但考慮到人群流動性大的春運即將來臨，有必要採取果斷措施盡快撲滅當前的疫情。<br />\n<br />\n1月12日，據河北省衛健委通報，11日0-24時，河北省新增40例本地新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診病例，其中石家莊市報告39例，廊坊市報告1例。<br />\n<br />\n河北省在1月12日下午的新冠肺炎疫情防控新聞發布會上通報稱，為防止疫情輸出，對石家莊市、邢台市、廊坊市全域實行封閉管理，人員、車輛非必要不外出。對三市中高風險地區的村莊和居民小區採取更為嚴格的封控措施，繼續嚴控人員流動。在公路、鐵路、城市客運、民航、水路等方面，採取最嚴格的管控措施。封住大交通，管控小交通，堅決防止重點地區人員流動，導致疫情向外傳播擴散。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，除了之前已出現多個確診病例的石家莊市和邢台市外，廊坊市也被列入封城名單中。廊坊市隨後發布通告稱，將在全市範圍內免費為全體市民做核酸檢測，全市進行為期七天的居家觀察。非必要不聚集。不舉辦廟會、燈會等大型聚集活動。不舉辦各類家庭、朋友、集體團拜等聚餐活動。<br />\n<br />\n除了河北省外，新冠疫情在黑龍江也呈擴散趨勢，其中疫情集中暴發的望奎縣12日宣布實行疫情防控最嚴格管控措施，住宅區全部實行封閉管理。同一天，黑龍江省多地發現望奎縣返鄉人員核酸檢測呈陽性。齊齊哈爾市12日通報​​稱，齊齊哈爾昂昂溪區對3名望奎縣返齊人員管控並核酸檢測陽性；對其密切接觸者同時進行排查檢測時，發現4名核酸檢測陽性人員。上述7人均為新冠肺炎無症狀感染者。伊春市12日通報​​，1名從望奎縣返鄉人員核酸檢測呈陽性，被確定為新冠肺炎無症狀感染者。哈爾濱12日晚也通報稱，發現1名從望奎縣返鄉人員為確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n多地接連封城，讓不少民眾回想起去年年初的情況。武漢大學醫學部病毒學研究所教授楊占秋12日對此表示，當下全國多地實施的封城和去年武漢的封城相比，封閉管理的做法上是相同的，但去年武漢實施封城的必要性跟現在的石家莊、邢台、廊坊相比要大得多，緊迫得多。 &ldquo;去年武漢封城之所以更為緊迫，是因為當時新冠疫情是在整個城市暴發流行，多點開花，病人數量也相當多，而且發病原因沒有搞清楚，誰也不知道是什麼病。相比而言，當前的石家莊等地，在實施封城的緊迫性上相比去年年初的武漢要小。<span class=\"red\">現在這幾個地區的病例加起來也就幾百例，而且已證實這一波疫情屬於輸入型感染，在源頭和病人的行踪上都是很清楚的，要控制疫情相對而言是比較容易的&rdquo;。</span>他表示，只要把密切接觸者、確診病例、無症狀感染者及相關的接觸人員控制好，就沒有什麼可擔心的。<br />\n<br />\n北京大學公共衛生學院副院長王培玉12日接受《環球時報》記者採訪時也認為，這次的封城和當初武漢不一樣，一是疫情遠沒武漢那麼嚴重，二是現在的檢測技術、防控策略經驗、救治水平都遠遠高於去年。<br />\n<br />\n楊占秋表示，宣布實施封閉管理是有科學依據的，同時還要考慮到封城對當地經濟社會發展、老百姓的生產生活各方面帶來的影響等綜合因素。他表示，目前河北三市及黑龍江望奎縣采取的封城措施可以理解。一方面，現在已經進入新冠病毒生長繁殖期，自然環境比較符合病毒的生存，發生疫情的這些城市都在北方；另一方面，春節馬上到了，考慮到人群流動性帶來的疫情擴散風險，有必要盡快撲滅疫情。 &ldquo;當下的封閉管理，也是為春節期間的人員流動提供更安全的環境&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n那麼這次封城會持續多長時間呢？楊占秋認為，當前在河北、黑龍江等地出現的不是本地疫情的暴發流行，是一種輸入型感染，傳播路徑也很清楚，病例範圍也很清楚。無論是疫情的程度還是疫情的性質都跟武漢完全不一樣。<span class=\"red\">所以當前封城措施持續的時間應該會比較短，&ldquo;現在距離春節還有一個月左右的時間，我覺得在春節前應該就會結束。</span>如果封城兩三週後，沒有新增確診病例了，可能到元月底就解封了，不會像武漢封那麼久&rdquo;。王培玉也表示，何時解除封城需要看今後的疫情走向，初步判斷應該在10天到14天左右。<br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：趙建東"},{"pid":"0bcb13549d5e828aa9eeeea05960782e4c82ba82","tid":2364552,"uid":51271,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"你咁講<strong>我仲驚</strong>"},{"pid":"0d434db645cde54020b96b5664f1534c1ef881e4","tid":2364552,"uid":127627,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"比武漢更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7678f9f69ceb08b1bfc73ad30aa1675ca9ff025","tid":2364552,"uid":337052,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"0bcb13549d5e828aa9eeeea05960782e4c82ba82","tid":2364552,"uid":51271,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"你咁講<strong>我仲驚</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"官媒闢謠<br />\n代表真的嚴重"},{"pid":"18c91ac91bebf5986fea125f85cc9e761d9cce89","tid":2364552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d434db645cde54020b96b5664f1534c1ef881e4","tid":2364552,"uid":127627,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"比武漢更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"係咪變種？"},{"pid":"6f3374bc2ae3a5a5ae92cc7ee0336e08773e8de2","tid":2364552,"uid":72713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"咁即係新病毒<br />\n石家莊肺炎？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7054a4e2d7b8aaedc03c3ac2ddea19184804c9cc","tid":2364552,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18c91ac91bebf5986fea125f85cc9e761d9cce89","tid":2364552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d434db645cde54020b96b5664f1534c1ef881e4","tid":2364552,"uid":127627,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"比武漢更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"係咪變種？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"有英國、南非、巴西和俄羅斯變種武漢肺炎輸入<br />\n應該沒有那麼簡單"},{"pid":"61ff3677e75fce618b582ec7be7fc12d25ba2061","tid":2364552,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"冇事=有事"},{"pid":"a2070408ec2b766aff1dff771d532dce5018fc44","tid":2364552,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:44:07.000Z","msg":"上年你都話武漢唔嚴重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d68b2b25543683f7132fba22ad9d0fcc54030e","tid":2364552,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"之前咪有張nyts同wh新年嘅對比嘅"},{"pid":"80166a09f8b0c4d1f7e56e06d03cd1e55373df47","tid":2364552,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"唔同 仲嚴重多幾百倍"},{"pid":"3a8ab02e057884d46764606ad71ab0ee3a36a352","tid":2364552,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"又可防可控丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bc32093fc0773d607ac9802c3939d9c0d04549","tid":2364552,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今次我撐你胡狗，的確不同！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要不同：河北天子腳下嘛！！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"236fad1eeb479b40c7431a7f96d317e3eb7cf08e","tid":2364552,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3a8ab02e057884d46764606ad71ab0ee3a36a352","tid":2364552,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"又可防可控丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSUXB77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSUXB77.jpg&h=6248f413&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d600d28371bf8b5095c093b8ee10972f310bf31d","tid":2364552,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"河北肺炎"},{"pid":"9050f864de51ba919ec09c70c8bff108227154db","tid":2364552,"uid":31017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"傳去中南海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n指日可待"},{"pid":"c0197c43bb7e2c74e1618a652bad02f169bc3380","tid":2364552,"uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XsbHhiE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXsbHhiE.png&h=0f9997b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UQCZIGr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUQCZIGr.png&h=7beb987b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5c80fa6cae6e1712c5c9609dc8f3b6661927cce","tid":2364552,"uid